    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>默契考验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >携手攀登，或一同坠落。《SunderBound》是一款双人合作的俯视角射击游戏，融合了roguelite元素与战术玩法。在这个因气候武器故障而崩坏的柴油朋克世界，你们的科技失灵，时间所剩无几，唯一的出路只有一层一层向上突破。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独裁者“部长”统治着巨型建筑“庇护所”。你们将作为反抗军，奋力向上攀爬。每一关都充满变数，敌人更强，陷阱更致命，抉择也更艰难。无论你选择与朋友并肩作战，还是与AI队友独自求生，都必须互相掩护，完美配合，并精准把握每次进攻的时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们必须这个世界中生存下来。也许在攀登的路上，还能顺手将它彻底粉碎。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双人体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《SunderBound》的核心在于合作。每次战斗、每次救援、每一个关键决策，都为双人模式量身打造。你可以选择本地联机、线上组队，或与AI队友同行。AI队友将始终跟随你，并听从你的指令。无论何种模式，团队协作才能一路向上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/ece40ab7460ea46ab1841bab091353f0.poster.avif?t=1769786106\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/ece40ab7460ea46ab1841bab091353f0.webm?t=1769786106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.avif?t=1769786106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras_big/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.webp?t=1769786106 width=1560 height=177 /></span><strong><br>硬核枪战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《SunderBound》的战斗在混乱中考验技巧。掩体至关重要。把握射击时机将决定你的生死。选择职业组合，分头包抄，精准执行每一次进攻。每道关卡都是一场压力测试。只要稍有慌乱，你将失去一切。计划得当，就能轻松碾压。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/84b6201dada334c5dc16cc53d7ef07c0.poster.avif?t=1769786106\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/84b6201dada334c5dc16cc53d7ef07c0.webm?t=1769786106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.avif?t=1769786106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras_big/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.webp?t=1769786106 width=1560 height=177 /></span><strong><br>层层血战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次任务都是一场艰难的攀登。由程序随机生成的关卡将不断变化，充满了埋伏、大批敌人和惊心动魄的Boss战。任务充满变数，你可探索不同的路径、敌人刷新点，以及改变玩法走向的能力。迅速上手，灵活应变，竭力突围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/0b004b558aec73593e641c77b8e29a2a.poster.avif?t=1769786106\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/0b004b558aec73593e641c77b8e29a2a.webm?t=1769786106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.avif?t=1769786106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras_big/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.webp?t=1769786106 width=1560 height=177 /></span><strong><br>风格由你定义</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个性化升级你的角色，获取、购买或打造适合你的装备。随着关卡不断推进，武器、能力和义体也可不断强化。与你的队友协同作战，探索各类全新战术。每一层推进都有其价值所在，每一点升级都将转化为更强的杀伤力、精准度和迅猛的攻势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/99d32f1f848b02e07f6a90240f6735ad.poster.avif?t=1769786106\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/99d32f1f848b02e07f6a90240f6735ad.webm?t=1769786106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.avif?t=1769786106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras_big/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.webp?t=1769786106 width=1560 height=177 /></span><strong><br>废墟美学</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘掉光洁的金属和简单的线条吧。这座巨塔粗犷而残破，充斥着紧张的气氛。裂开的水泥、裸露的电线和闪烁的警示灯点缀着每个角落。你将一路深入，穿越蒸汽弥漫的工厂、坍塌的医疗站和废弃的实验室。一切都粗粝而紧凑，却又恰到好处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/3f0c701604f36c3e1df0ddca2fccd7fa.poster.avif?t=1769786106\" width=780 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/3f0c701604f36c3e1df0ddca2fccd7fa.webm?t=1769786106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.avif?t=1769786106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477750/extras_big/70083844fd3d879813f7d127f1ea28ad.webp?t=1769786106 width=1560 height=177 /></span></p>",
